How is this possible 😳🤯 @nycmayor @devontemagic

Some kids want to be lawyers, some want to play basketball, all I ever wanted was to share my magic with the world. 

Born n raised in Bushwick Brooklyn NY,  8 year old me dreamt of one day sharing my magic for thousands of people live and on TV. Like the greats before me (Houdini, Blaine, Copperfield)

Sometimes you’re so busy focused on reaching your dreams and goals that you forget to notice how far you’ve come. It’s easy to see what’s not going right, but it takes a moment of gratitude to realize you are exactly where you need to be. 

If you’re reading this, you need to keep going. You need to trust the process, don’t give up now! If 2023 put you through challenges, just know that you’re still standing for a reason, it was preparation for what’s coming your life. Stay strong, stay focused! 🙏🏽🫡
